## Setup recap

- **Cohort**: 18 tickers × 2 Fridays = 36 propagates (NVDA, MSFT, AAPL, WFC, MA, COP, INTC, GOOGL, AMD, AMZN, AVGO, BAC, CSCO, GS, JPM, LLY, CVX, HON × 2026-04-17 + 2026-04-24)
- **Boost configuration**: ENABLED (window=14d, magnitude=0.5x, T_bull=0.60)
- **Boost-OFF comparison**: post-hoc reconstruction from state-log `bull_case_priced_in > T_bull AND pre_rating in {Buy, Overweight}`
- **Compute**: started 2026-05-07 06:14 PDT; completed [TIMESTAMP]; total wall-clock [HRS] hours
- **LLM cost**: actual ~$[X.XX] (estimated $18 in HYPOTHESIS.md)

