## Per-row decomposition

Of the **[XX]** rows where boost CHANGED the decision (`fired_boost_on != would_fire_boost_off`):
- Cohort-correct fires (boosted into Hold + realized α was negative): [XX]
- False-positive fires (boosted into Hold + realized α was positive): [XX]

The boost contribution to net Δα is computed only over the boost-changed-decision rows. Spec 007 alone contribution = (boost-OFF kept α − bull baseline α). Spec 008 marginal contribution = (boost-ON kept α − boost-OFF kept α).

